          </a>

          <a href="https://x.com/deexonsolutions" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group relative flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10">
            <img src="/icon/twitter-original.svg" alt="Twitter" class="w-5 h-5" />
          </a>
